{"tid":1881041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鑽石公主號新增67宗武漢肺炎確診 東京新增8宗 本土合計52宗","createTime":"2020-02-15T09:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T10:03:51.000Z","uid":254183,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ec1cc23c2f44eaa69af6489fe54ecd96d81924","tid":1881041,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"日本武漢肺炎疫情持續擴大，厚生勞動省表示，「鑽石公主號」郵輪15日新增67宗確診案例。同時，東京都也新確診8宗病例。<br />\n<br />\n《NHK》報導，東京都知情人士透露，這8名新病例的其中7人，和13日確診的計程車司機有過密切接觸。報導指出，超過100人和該司機曾有過密切接觸，因此受到東京都的調查，這才發現另外7個確診病例。目前，日本本土有52宗確診案例。<br />\n<br />\n厚生勞動大臣加藤勝信在記者會上指出，至今無法掌握13日以降的多個新冠肺炎患者傳染路徑，「這與之前的狀況不同」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，日本厚生勞動省表示，「鑽石公主號」郵輪今日新增67宗確診案例，當中38人未出現症狀。該郵輪已出現285宗確診案例。<br />\n<br />\n５２：５６<br />\n港隊快被日本隊超越了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0125db34651104bc95be1008c33e36f8fa2a7dab","tid":1881041,"uid":59617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efu45rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fefu45rz.jpg&h=ba93b112&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"438a80a8411ea3774bc45f9351e53f620ac0ddaa","tid":1881041,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f197c5e307315549800880d3f805a18d379f67","tid":1881041,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"日本仲爆得勁過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592e76108bd47436caf4d2b81ee824425afa7da6","tid":1881041,"uid":26071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0125d